highlights.text: “愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 179 days straight.
“ĐƯA EM VÀO TRÒNG” by 2pillz, GDucky, and tlinh is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #85.
EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “KHÔNG ĐAU NỮA RỒI” is the highest at #34.
“Montagem Supersonic” by KHAOS and Jmilton is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 20 spots at #51.
